"title": "8287: joy, and human experience",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8287",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Joy is experienced naturally in many circumstances of life and in human relationships. It is especially important in the life of God's people, who experience joy in response to all that God has done for them.</p>\n<h2>Poetic images of joy in creation</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps96:11-Ps96:13\">PSA 96:11–96:13</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr16:31-1Chr16:33\">1CH 16:31–16:33</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job39:13\">JOB 39:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps65:12-Ps65:13\">PSA 65:12–65:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps89:12\">PSA 89:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps97:1\">PSA 97:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps100:1\">PSA 100:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa35:1-Isa35:2\">ISA 35:1–35:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa49:13\">ISA 49:13</a></p>\n<h2>Joy arising from specific circumstances</h2>\n<h3>Joy because of the birth of children</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:13-Luke1:15\">LUK 1:13–1:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen30:12-Gen30:13\">GEN 30:12–30:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:58\">LUK 1:58</a></p>\n<h3>Joy because of victory and deliverance</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod18:9\">EXO 18:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam18:6\">1SA 18:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer41:13\">JER 41:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech10:7\">ZEC 10:7</a></p>\n<h3>Joy because of the behaviour of others</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:30\">PRO 15:30</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov23:24-Prov23:25\">PRO 23:24–23:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt14:6-Matt14:7\">MAT 14:6–14:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:17\">HEB 13:17</a></p>\n<h3>Joy because of God's blessings in everyday life</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl5:19-Eccl5:20\">ECC 5:19–5:20</a></strong></p>\n<h2>Joy arising from relationships</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:1\">PHP 4:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov5:18\">PRO 5:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song1:4\">SNG 1:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song3:11\">SNG 3:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:15\">ROM 12:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:26-Rom15:27\">ROM 15:26–15:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:26\">1CO 12:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:4-Phil1:6\">PHP 1:4–1:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phlm1:7\">PHM 1:7</a></p>\n<h2>God's people find their joy in him</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps4:7\">PSA 4:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps16:11\">PSA 16:11</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab3:17-Hab3:18\">HAB 3:17–3:18</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:1\">PHP 3:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr16:10\">1CH 16:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps43:4\">PSA 43:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:23-Phil1:26\">PHP 1:23–1:26</a> <em>knowing Jesus Christ</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:4\">PHP 4:4</a></p>\n<h3>God himself gives joy to his people</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh12:43\">NEH 12:43</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job8:21\">JOB 8:21</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl2:26\">ECC 2:26</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa9:3\">ISA 9:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:52\">ACT 13:52</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:15-Acts14:17\">ACT 14:15–14:17</a></p>\n<h3>Reasons for God's people to know joy</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam2:1\">1SA 2:1</a> <em>God's deliverance</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr6:41\">2CH 6:41</a> <em>God's goodness</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job22:22-Job22:26\">JOB 22:22–22:26</a> <em>repentance</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps19:8\">PSA 19:8</a> <em>the rightness of God's precepts</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps94:19\">PSA 94:19</a> <em>God's consolation</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps122:1\">PSA 122:1</a> <em>being in God's presence</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa25:9\">ISA 25:9</a> <em>God's salvation</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa58:13-Isa58:14\">ISA 58:13–58:14</a> <em>honouring the Sabbath</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer15:16\">JER 15:16</a> <em>God's words</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:12\">JER 31:12</a> <em>God's generosity</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:46-Luke1:49\">LUK 1:46–1:49</a> <em>recognition by God</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:13\">ROM 15:13</a> <em>trusting God</em></p>",
